-suspicions-she-has-in-the-past-made-statements-referring-to-former-professional-baseball-player/">VTuber Mirei Gundo怀疑“我不了解棒球规则” 一些言论涉及过去的前职业棒球运动员</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“VTuber群道美玲对‘我不知道棒球规则’表示怀疑，并曾发表过提及前职业棒球运动员的言论” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-gundo-mirei-unfamiliarity-with-baseball-rules-attitude-is-raising-suspicions-she-has-in-the-past-made-statements-referring-to-former-professional-baseball-player/embed/#?secret=Koy4dmA9aK#?secret=zaRhDYjFnn" data-secret="zaRhDYjFnn" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><p>此外，有消息称，Gundo 先生涉嫌在其仅限会员的发行版中进行所谓的“蓝鲸”行为。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="g2VMwAeo91"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/some-roundup-blogs-have-published-the-alleged-blue-whale-challenge-of-vtuber-gundo-mirei-also-spreading-on-sns/">部分摘要网站VTuber发布疑似军藤美玲的“蓝鲸”行为是否在SNS上传播？</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“部分摘要网站 VTuber Gundo Mirei 涉嫌‘蓝鲸’行为被发布，是否在 SNS 上传播？” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/some-roundup-blogs-have-published-the-alleged-blue-whale-challenge-of-vtuber-gundo-mirei-also-spreading-on-sns/embed/#?secret=k3mQ5ltRf6#?secret=g2VMwAeo91" data-secret="g2VMwAeo91" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="M1NlCj4Afh"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/some-news-media-report-on-nijisanji-vtuber-gundo-mireis-alleged-blue-whale-challenge-this-appears-to-have-appeared-in-nifty-news-and-elsewhere/">部分媒体《Nijisanji》所属VTuber Gundo Mirei报道了涉嫌“蓝鲸”行为的Nifty News等。</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“一些媒体《Nijisanji》所属的 VTuber Gundo Mirei 报道了涉嫌“蓝鲸”行为的 Nifty 新闻等” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/some-news-media-report-on-nijisanji-vtuber-gundo-mireis-alleged-blue-whale-challenge-this-appears-to-have-appeared-in-nifty-news-and-elsewhere/embed/#?secret=sKDeTzpZIQ#?secret=M1NlCj4Afh" data-secret="M1NlCj4Afh" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><p>在这种情况下，ANYCOLOR宣布米莉·贡多“毕业”，不仅是因为最初关于WBC的争议言论、前述“过去的问题行为和怀疑”，还因为SNS毕业后立即关闭。观众和粉丝猜测合同几乎被取消而不是友好毕业。</p><p> Mirei Gundo 的最后一次分娩是在 6 月 21 日 23:00 进行的。 </p><p></p><div class="ctgsa64b515015356d" ><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-3186024119059876"
